description: The charity event has been called off as authorities said its risk factor was "unacceptably high".
title: Coronavirus: Jersey Swimarathon cancelled after first case confirmed
title_page: Coronavirus: Jersey Swimarathon cancelled after first case confirmed - BBC News
maintext: "We don't know what is going to happen, we have cancelled it rather than postponed it because what we couldn't judge was when we had to postpone it to," Mr Tabb said.
